import StringAlgebra.MZV.Motivic.Core
import StringAlgebra.MZV.Motivic.Interfaces

/-!
# Motivic Multiple Zeta Values

This module re-exports the motivic development from the `Motivic/` subfolder.
The core motivic model lives in `Motivic/Core.lean`, while toy period/Galois
interfaces are isolated in `Motivic/Interfaces.lean`.

Archived low-weight sample calculations are kept out of the library surface in
ignored local scratch files under `test/local/`.

Import `StringAlgebra.MZV.Motivic.Core` directly if you want only the motivic
infrastructure.
-/
